PrecisOrder which (a) accepts the transfer from the Province of BRITISH COLUMBIA of administration and control over some 165 acres of land situate in the District of Campbell River, and (b) sets them apart for the use and benefit of the HOMALCO BAND OF INDIANS as a reserve to be known as "HOMALCO INDIAN RESERVE NO. 9".
